sequenceDiagram
    actor Employee as Працівник
    actor Manager as Manager/Admin
    participant App as Flutter app
    participant ApiService
    participant API as FastAPI payroll routes
    participant Files as uploads/
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant TG as Telegram Bot API

    Employee->>App: Заповнює payroll report
    App->>ApiService: submitPayrollReport(objectName, comment, files)
    ApiService->>API: POST /payroll multipart/form-data
    API->>DB: insert PayrollReport
    loop файли
        API->>Files: write upload
        API->>DB: insert PayrollMedia
    end
    API->>DB: commit
    API->>DB: select users role admin/superadmin
    loop admins
        API->>TG: send payroll notification
    end
    API-->>ApiService: PayrollReportResponse

    Manager->>App: Переглядає reports
    App->>ApiService: GET /payroll/reports
    ApiService->>API: GET /payroll/reports?object_name=&is_checked=
    API->>DB: select PayrollReport with media/user
    API-->>ApiService: reports
    Manager->>App: Позначає перевіреним
    App->>ApiService: POST /payroll/{report_id}/check
    ApiService->>API: POST /payroll/{report_id}/check
    API->>DB: set is_checked=true
